<h1 align="center">The CLASS Tour</h1>
<h2 align="center">Workshop on tools for cosmology: the <a href="http://class-code.net" target="new">CLASS</a> and <a href="http://montepython.net" target="new">Monte Python</a> codes</h2>
<h3 align="center"> by Benjamin Audren, Julien Lesgourgues, Thomas Tram </h3>
<h4 align="center"> with the kind participation of Jesus Torrado & Miguel Zumalacarregui </h4>
<h4 align="center">
[UNAM, Mexico City, 14-17 Octobre 2013]
[MPA, Munich, 17-21 March 2014]
[Uni. Geneva, 31 March - 03 April 2014]
</h4>
<h4 align="center">
[King's & UCL, London, 11-16 May 2014]
[Barcelona, TBC, Octobre 2014]
[Kavli IPMU, Tokyo, 27-31 Octobre 2014]</h4>
<br>

